            <h2 class="card-title">Objectives</h2>
            <p class="card-text">In our terms, the objective of any good recipe is continuity â€“ clear enough direction for anyone to recreate the same dish, no matter who or where they are, with identical results.<br>Futhermore, It is meant to include the technical aspects of a dish while also teaching the artistic combination of flavor and texture. A recipe communicates the ingredients and procedures the chef uses to make his creations</p>
