<ul>
  <li>The name of the recipe (Origins/History of the dish).</li>
    <li>  Yield: The number of servings that the dish provides.</li>
     <li>  List all ingredients in the order of its use. Describe it in step by step instructions.</li>
</ul></p>
          </div>
